name: Cardinal Energy Ltd. 8.25% senior subordinated unsecured debentures
longDescription: Cardinal Energy Ltd. is an oil focused Canadian company built to provide investors with sustainable yield and growth. Management is focused on a disciplined growth plan both financially and operationally while providing a sustainable dividend to its Shareholders.
